                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 80 cm3 Ge(Li) detector was placed at an angle",
                "of 90 degr. at a distance of 2.4 cm from the beam axis",
                "for gamma-ray transitions.",
                "There were also used Ge(Li) detectors placed around the",
                "cylindrical jet target chamber at angles of 39, 90 and",
                "116 degrees at a distance of 5-6 cm from the jet",
                "stream axis.",
                "The beam current was monitored with standard current",
                "integration as well as elastic scattering yields",
                "observed at the angle of 35, 90 and 145 degr. in the",
                "laboratory system."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Neon gas enriched to 99.99% in 20Ne was recirculated",
                "in differentially pumped gas target systems of the",
                "extended and quasipoint jet types.",
                "For neon gas of p0=2.0 Torr pressure in the target",
                "chamber, the pressure was reduced to 1*10E-2, 1*10E-3",
                "and 1*10E-6 Torr in the first, second and third",
                "pumping stages of the system, respectively."
              ]
            }
